    <section id="VCL+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>VCL Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="graduated">The VCL project graduated on 2012-06-20</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>
          VCL is a management framework for building, dispensing and managing virtual machine
          images across a set of bare metal machines or systems with an installed virtual machine hypervisor.
      </p>
    </section>
